- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is possible because the paper discusses a method for defining functions using previously computed values, which could be relevant to software engineering.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is possible because the paper deals with formalizing and manipulating inductive datatypes, which could be relevant to formal languages and automata theory.
